{"tid":1367702,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（元朗遊行）休息站 朗屏宣道會天頌堂(虹方301)休息空間","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:34.000Z","uid":290791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5636ff096592d99942255294fa949c083cd87e47","tid":1367702,"uid":290791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"7.27 宣道會天頌堂(虹方301)休息空間<br />\n<br />\n因應7.27本週六元朗遊行及近期社會情況的需要，教會將虹方301室開放作為休息空間，供有需要人士使用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開放時間：7.27本週六 下午三時至晚上十時。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n地址：元朗宏業南街22號虹方大廈301室（朗屏<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">西鐵站F出口對面</span></span>）<br />\n<br />\n場地功能：作有需要人士安憩休息、飲水、去洗手間之用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">義工支援：傾談關心、代禱服侍、提供合適的交通資訊。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n電話：2479 0154"},{"pid":"a42688605e52e92600226fe0449c06bd14f0b526","tid":1367702,"uid":290791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93895acd6f13f1bd1b4f59c09df1b064c99de282","tid":1367702,"uid":290791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9e0856fc1ba49e97597e3d518fbf34258dfdbce","tid":1367702,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}